summary: This document includes a dispatch regarding contact reports from Peter J. DI GERVENO concerning his meetings with AMCLOCK/1 in September 1967. The reports detail AMCLOCK/1's activities, observations, and intelligence production, including his views on the PBRUMEN government and security matters.
title: Transmittal of Contact Reports for First Two Meetings with AMCLOCK/1
recipient: Chief, WH/Cuba; COS, JMWAVE; Chief, DOD; Chief of Base, New York
